ral for home care services would be considered the date of referral. \n\nOASIS-E1 \nEffective 01/01/2025 \nCenters for Medicare & Medicaid Services \n\n34 \n\n![Mo104.DateofReferral\nIndicate the date that the written or verbal referral for initiation or resumption of care was received by the HHA.\nMonth\nYear](#)\n\fChapter 3 \n\nSection A: Administrative Information", "type": "Document"}}